column2: select s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, l.logMass, l.cModelAbsMag_r from SpecObj as s, PhotoObj as p, stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust as l, dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) as n where s.specObjID = l.specObjID AND s.bestObjID = n.objID AND s.specObjID = p.specObjID AND p.objID = n.objID AND s.z BETWEEN # and #AND s.ra BETWEEN # and # AND s.dec BETWEEN # and # AND l.cModelAbsMag_r <= #
